metadata.description:
Bitz are the original 1000 supply holders only, private discord club.

Online and offline rewards will be given to these holders, and no more will ever be made to keep this exclusiveness.

Each Bitz is a 16x16 handmade Pixel Art by Punkie.

There are 1000 in total:

- 800 Bitz
- 50 Pigz
- 50 Chickenz
- 30 Robotz
- 30 Devilz
- 25 Zombiez
- 10 Alienz
- 5 Shadowz
